8I4.F.summary: Nurminen Logistics Oyj provides logistics services in Finland, Russia, and Baltic countries. The company provides forwarding, cargo handling, and value added services, as well as railway transport and related project transport services to its customers. It also provides terminal services, warehousing, and project logistics services. The company was founded in 1886 and is headquartered in Helsinki, Finland.
